Interface GeoLoc

All Superinterfaces:
SonarObject
All Known Implementing Classes:
GeoLocImpl, IncidentLoc, TransGeoLoc
public interface GeoLoc extends SonarObject
GeoLoc contains attributes necessary to describe a map location.
Author:
Douglas Lau, Travis Swanston
